584
00:48:59,390 --> 00:49:00,558
Samantha!

585
00:49:02,560 --> 00:49:04,604
<i>Talvez eu esteja morta no inferno.</i>

586
00:49:05,063 --> 00:49:07,315
<i>Talvez eu esteja viva no inferno.</i>

587
00:49:08,358 --> 00:49:09,651
<i>Mas não importava.</i>

588
00:49:10,777 --> 00:49:12,570
<i>Nada mais importava.</i>

589
00:49:16,783 --> 00:49:18,159
