639
00:52:25,179 --> 00:52:27,598
Vá se sentar.
Por favor.

640
00:52:27,932 --> 00:52:29,225
Já que insiste.

641
00:52:35,023 --> 00:52:37,275
Certo. Sísifo.

642
00:52:42,071 --> 00:52:46,034
